channel.title: Help just an error, read and try to help
channel.description:
Hey, it's me again lol. I got a little error wonderin' if you guys can help out, here it is client.java:28616: illegal start of expression if((id == 15333) || (id == 15334) || (id == 15335) || (id == 15336)) || (id == 1 6000)) // Godswords. ^ client.java:28616: ';' expected if((id == 15333) || (id == 15334) || (id == 15335) || (id == 15336)) || (id == 1 6000)) // Godswords.
^ 2 errors Finished! Press any key to continue . . .
when compiling this happens
Thanks :D
edit: btw id 16000 is a custom gs i made. I was trying to add it
